brett takes your breath away if i was going to hire an escort he is the one i would want . penelope and brett made a great couple . her father -in- law wanted her to date again after losing her husband on a bucking bull . she has to convince him she has a boyfriend so he quits sending every eligible bachelor in town to her office . brett shows up and steals the show . he stands up to her father -in-law and wins the respect of the whole town . this is an excellent movie